          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "/by Authors/.The Data in Table were Obtained from Two",
                "Separate Bombardments.The Absolute Energy of the Proton",
                "Was not Known For the First Bombardment, so these data",
                "Were Fit Into That of the Second Bombardment by",
                "Matching Threshold Energies.The Absolute Amount of",
                "Bismuth was Known Only For a Few Plates of Run 1, So",
                "Only the Ratio Sigma(P,2N)/(SIGMA(P,N)+SIGMA(P,2N)) Is",
                "Given at Many of the Energies."
              ]
            }
          ],
